Dogface Soldier   also

Baker Boys: Inside the Surge – 2010 documentary about a company in 3d ID.
Dogface – term referring to soldiers of the 3d ID.
Heavy Metal: a Tank Company's Battle to Baghdad – 2005 book co-written by former 3d ID company commander.
Over There – 2005 fictional television series about a 3d ID unit.
To Hell and Back – 1955 film based on Audie Murphy's 1949 autobiography novel.
256th Infantry Brigade – US Army unit attached to 3d ID in OIF III.
